// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0062 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: baf1fb90-c755-541e-bd63-f97081005cf9

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:2* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
